parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The complete failure of the electric vehicle battery can leave the driver stranded, causing inconvenience and potential safety risks.
symptoms: The vehicle will not operate
unable to start or move.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose braking power, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the brake pedal sticks to the floor
the vehicle loses braking power
warning lights illuminate on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the backup camera can reduce visibility while reversing, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The backup camera display is blank or intermittent
the camera fails to display when in reverse
the screen turns pink or displays static lines.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the 12V battery can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
warning lights illuminate on the dashboard
the vehicle is unable to start or move.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause distractions while driving, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The infotainment screen reboots multiple times
the navigation map turns black
the rear camera video is grayed out
poor audio quality during phone calls.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Clutch and Parking Brake System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and parking brake system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The brake warning sign comes off
the vehicle won't shift out of parking brake
the clutch pedal feels soft or spongy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power supply system can cause the vehicle to lose power, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle loses power
screens display "Power Supply Failure" and "When parked apply parking brake" while driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear camera can cause reduced visibility while backing up, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The rear camera displays a blank screen
shows a black screen
displays green and pink static lines
or has horizontal lines that interfere with the view.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The inaccurate DTE calculation can cause driver distraction, leading to potential safety issues.
symptoms: The DTE calculation dramatically drops after 100 miles of driving
prematurely alerting the driver that the battery is depleted when it is not.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent throttle sticking can cause loss of vehicle control, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The throttle sticks wide open and does not release
requiring the driver to stomp on the brake pedal and make several attempts to release the throttle.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The air conditioning system throttling can cause dangerously hot temperatures in the vehicle, especially in the back seat, leading to potential health risks.
symptoms: The air conditioning system reduces power to conserve battery life
causing temperatures to rise above 100 degrees in the vehicle
especially in heavy traffic or stop-and-go conditions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The infotainment system resetting can cause the backup camera to malfunction, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The infotainment system frequently resets
causing the backup camera to not display
and occurring often within 10 seconds of starting the car.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rearview camera can cause a blind spot, making it difficult to back up safely, and increasing the risk of accidents or injuries to pedestrians or children.
symptoms: The rearview camera display shows a black screen
the camera works intermittently
the camera does not work at all
the rear blind spot warning system does not function.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The defrosting and defogging system issues can cause reduced visibility while driving, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The defroster limits visibility out of the windshield under cold conditions
the windshield does not properly defrost
the windshield is foggy
and the defrosting system does not function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The infotainment system issues can cause distractions while driving, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The climate control status is not visible on the screen when using Android Auto
the climate control settings cannot be easily adjusted
the system requires multiple touchscreen interactions to adjust settings.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rear hatchback window shattering can cause injuries or damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: The rear hatchback window shatters when the hatch is closed with normal force
without any objects obstructing closure or touching the window.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The wiper system failure can cause reduced visibility while driving, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The wipers stop working
